body: $TNT With respect to the SEC processing time
created_at: below is a list of known timeline:

body: TNT submits 40-F   2021-10-27
SEC first comments  2021-11-24 (+28 days)
TNT submits 40-F amendment 2021-12-7 (+13 days)
SEC second comments 2021-12-28 (+21 days)
TNT submits response letter 2022-1-12 (+15 days)

According to this 2013 statistics https://www.wilmerhale.com/en/insights/blogs/the-road-to-ipo-legal-and-regulatory-insights-into-going-public/how-quickly-does-the-sec-staff-review-a-form-s-1-updated-data

column3: I think we are perfectly within the normal SEC processing time.
